CatDescriptText: Westinghouse High School star Allen Lee attempts a rebound against opposing team on the basketball court at Fifth Avenue High School.  The audience watches as both teams jump for the basketball, the referee runs along side of the court to catch the play.  Photograph was possibly taken for City Sports in 1961.
TitMainTitle: Basketball game, possibly between Westinghouse and Fifth Avenue High School, with players jumping at hoop
